The paper discusses deep learning models and their behavior, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on language translation and parsing, which are subfields of natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of statistical methods to identify hidden units in neural networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions object recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses recurrent neural networks, which are a type of neural network commonly used in the field of neural engineering (cs.NE).
